= toolbox-copilot
Al Idian <al.idian@acm.org>
:description: Containerized development environments with Copilot

The latest image is compatible with:

* linux/amd64
* linux/arm64

Usage:

[source,bash]
----
# Build and push images to Docker Hub
docker buildx build \
    --platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 \
    -t idianal/toolbox-copilot:latest \
    -t idianal/toolbox-copilot:<version> \
    --push \
    -f dockerfile \
    .

# Start a toolbox container using Docker
docker run --rm -it idianal/toolbox-ai
----
